          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0632P0_20020321_GCR_43' title='Link to this speech by Mr Kenneth Wedderburn' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-kenneth-wedderburn" title="Mr Kenneth Wedderburn">Lord Wedderburn of Charlton</a></cite>
