      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0632P0-04768'>
        <a name='S5LV0632P0_20020321_GCR_47'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-kenneth-wedderburn' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0632P0_20020321_GCR_47' title='Link to this speech by Mr Kenneth Wedderburn' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-kenneth-wedderburn" title="Mr Kenneth Wedderburn">Lord Wedderburn of Charlton</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
            Is it working now?
          </p>
